data.name: KeyStroke
desc: Describes a key stroke for hotkeys etc.

properties.name: Modifiers
desc: contains the modifier keys which were pressed while the event occurred.
Zero or more constants from the group com.sun.star.awt.KeyModifier.

properties.name: KeyCode
desc: contains the integer code representing the key of the event.
This is a constant from the constant group com.sun.star.awt.Key.

properties.name: KeyChar
desc: contains the Unicode character generated by this event or 0.

properties.name: KeyFunc
desc: contains the function type of the key event.
This is a constant from the constant group com.sun.star.awt.KeyFunction.
